item.title: Privacy
item.description: Privacy Policy Your privacy is important to us. It is MobileOrg’s policy to respect your privacy regarding any information we may collect from you through the app, MobileOrg. We never intend to collect or store your personal information. Any personal information is only collected when it is a part of the default iOS SDKs in order to provide support to you. We only retain collected information for as long as necessary to provide you with your requested service.
